metadata.description:
Created in partnership with Chafomon, the $WHALE White Paper Series NFTs capture a monumental point in $WHALE history, the release of the $WHALE White Paper.

The WhaleShark Autograph is a $WHALE Collectible that captures both the $WHALE Icon graphic created by Murat Pak, the original $WHALE key visual, "Old Money" (Avastars #63) and WhaleShark's personal signature.

This is an edition of 10.
metadata.name: $WHALE White Paper - WhaleShark Autograph
